      • isFinalEvaluated

        private boolean isFinalEvaluated
        This flag keeps track if final evaluations are calculated for each individual submitted document from their possibly multiple evaluations. This flag will be made true when Coductor clicks on "disseminating grades" to students // or while calculating fairness of grades - currently its done during "disseminating grades" to students.

      • finalEvalType

        private EvalType finalEvalType
        The default EvalType - for final Evaluation calculation for submitted documents; This can be changed while - a) Disseminating grades to students or b) while calculating fairness of grades IMP - Currently it is done - while Disseminating grades to students, as fairness calculation is a future work of this project
